The Plugged In S1 link up series has taken the drill world by storm, featuring big names and up comers in drill rap it has grabbed the attention of millions of fans across the world.

The A92 freestyle is one of the more particularly popular freestyles grossing 20 million views on YouTube and over 50 million Spotify plays. Featuring A92’s best: BT, KSav, Dbo and Offica. The freestyle brought drill rap more attention and gave a high expectation for the next Plugged in freestyle.
